title: Lil Yachty Shows Off Some of the Rarest Jordans and Nike SBs on Part 2 Of Complex Closets
author: Complex
description:
Lil Yachty is back on Complex Closets and for Part 2 he shows Joe La Puma some of his rarest and most expensive sneakers, including 1985 Air Jordan 1s, never-released Air Jordan PEs, and reveals the sneakers he's still hunting down.

Looking for the best deal on a pair of sneakers? Download the Sole Collector app now!: https://solecollector.com/app
